    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_5_495-510",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "495-510",
      "markText": "我感到不舒适，所以我是存在的。",
      "totalCount": 1134,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025954&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=495&rangeEnd=510",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9c132ba0813ab70a3g014412?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=495&rangeEnd=510"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_4_1980-2030",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1980-2030",
      "markText": "我还没死，但也不算是活的了。 ——但丁",
      "totalCount": 1034,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025954&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1980&rangeEnd=2030",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9c132ba0813ab70a3g014412?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1980&rangeEnd=2030"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_6_4398-4437",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4398-4437",
      "markText": "“一个人要是没有别的东西可以向人夸耀，”院长说，“就只有炫耀自己的精神苦闷了。",
      "totalCount": 616,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025954&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4398&rangeEnd=4437",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9c132ba0813ab70a3g014412?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4398&rangeEnd=4437"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_5_7422-7446",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "7422-7446",
      "markText": "痛苦是一种只要你需要，随时就可以提供给你的东西。",
      "totalCount": 384,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025954&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7422&rangeEnd=7446",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9c132ba0813ab70a3g014412?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7422&rangeEnd=7446"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_6_5136-5173",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5136-5173",
      "markText": "“人们对于《圣经》上的东西，只是挑选他们愿意相信的才记住，真是太遗憾了。”",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025954&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5136&rangeEnd=5173",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9c132ba0813ab70a3g014412?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5136&rangeEnd=5173"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_6_7089-7135",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7089-7135",
      "markText": "一个老处女，没有独自的精神世界，一心要做好事，要替别人服务。世界上为这种人安排的地方并不多。",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025954&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7089&rangeEnd=7135",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9c132ba0813ab70a3g014412?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7089&rangeEnd=7135"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_7_3955-3964",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3955-3964",
      "markText": "我永远也不往回走了",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025954&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3955&rangeEnd=3964",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9c132ba0813ab70a3g014412?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3955&rangeEnd=3964"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_5_6472-6509",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "6472-6509",
      "markText": "他被遗弃在自己的天地内。在他的领域，笑声好像是敌人的语言，他是无法听懂的。",
      "totalCount": 264,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025954&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6472&rangeEnd=6509",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9c132ba0813ab70a3g014412?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6472&rangeEnd=6509"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_5_2055-2124",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2055-2124",
      "markText": "旅客即使把衣服全部脱光也热得无法入睡，而且他无论如何也拿不定主意，是应该开着门窗通进一点儿气流呢，还是应该把门窗关紧，不叫外边的热气进来。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025954&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2055&rangeEnd=2124",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9c132ba0813ab70a3g014412?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2055&rangeEnd=2124"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_5_2868-2879",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2868-2879",
      "markText": "蚊子并不怜悯瘦人。’”",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025954&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2868&rangeEnd=2879",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9c132ba0813ab70a3g014412?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2868&rangeEnd=2879"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_5_4439-4482",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4439-4482",
      "markText": "这位神父有着嗜杀癖，不论看到什么野生动物都要开枪，倒仿佛只有人类才有权利不遭横杀似的。",
      "totalCount": 247,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025954&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4439&rangeEnd=4482",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9c132ba0813ab70a3g014412?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4439&rangeEnd=4482"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_18_24104-24139",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "24104-24139",
      "markText": "他想：国王死了，国王万岁。可能他在这里又找到了一个国度，也找到了生活。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025954&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=24104&rangeEnd=24139",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9c132ba0813ab70a3g014412?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=24104&rangeEnd=24139"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_15_13440-13504",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "13440-13504",
      "markText": "我认识到自己根本没有爱情只不过是个时间问题。我从来没有真正爱过人。我只是接受别人的爱。从这以后我对生活就开始感到无法忍受的厌腻。",
      "totalCount": 238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025954&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=13440&rangeEnd=13504",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9c132ba0813ab70a3g014412?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=13440&rangeEnd=13504"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_15_19710-19749",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "19710-19749",
      "markText": "在人的一生中常常有一段时间，只要他有一点儿演戏的才能，就会连他自己也欺骗过去。",
      "totalCount": 231,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025954&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=19710&rangeEnd=19749",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9c132ba0813ab70a3g014412?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=19710&rangeEnd=19749"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_8_2170-2196",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2170-2196",
      "markText": "莱克尔说他相信爱情就像有些人说他们相信神话故事似的。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025954&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2170&rangeEnd=2196",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9c132ba0813ab70a3g014412?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2170&rangeEnd=2196"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_17_10297-10324",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "10297-10324",
      "markText": "“你这个人太谦虚了，这是你高贵的品质。”托马斯神父说。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025954&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=10297&rangeEnd=10324",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9c132ba0813ab70a3g014412?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=10297&rangeEnd=10324"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_5_831-874",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "831-874",
      "markText": "如果没有变化就意味着宁静，他们这样像果仁似的被包裹在不舒适的硬壳中心，就确实在享受宁静",
      "totalCount": 220,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025954&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=831&rangeEnd=874",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9c132ba0813ab70a3g014412?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=831&rangeEnd=874"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025954_5_6844-6879",
